<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Our Founders | Baribaba</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; }
    body { background:#f7f7f7; color:#222; }

    header { background:#fff; padding:16px 60px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
    header img { height:40px; }
    nav a { margin-left:25px; text-decoration:none; color:#222; font-weight:500; }
    nav a:hover { color:#d81f26; }

    .hero { background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.55),rgba(0,0,0,.55)), url('assets/images/hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; padding:90px 60px; color:#fff; text-align:center; }
    .hero h1 { font-size:42px; margin-bottom:10px; }
    .hero p { font-size:18px; max-width:700px; margin:auto; }

    section { padding:80px 60px; }

    .founders { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr)); gap:40px; max-width:1100px; margin:auto; }

    .founder { background:#fff; padding:40px; border-radius:18px; box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .founder img { width:140px; height:140px; border-radius:50%; object-fit:cover; margin-bottom:20px; }
    .founder h2 { margin-bottom:6px; }
    .role { color:#d81f26; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:15px; }
    .founder p { color:#555; line-height:1.8; }

    .vision { background:#fff; border-radius:18px; padding:50px; max-width:900px; margin:80px auto 0; box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.1); text-align:center; }
    .vision h3 { font-size:30px; margin-bottom:15px; }
    .vision p { color:#555; line-height:1.8; }

    footer { background:#111; color:#aaa; text-align:center; padding:35px; margin-top:80px; }

    @media(max-width:768px){
      header, section, .hero { padding:40px 25px; }
      .hero h1 { font-size:32px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <img src="assets/images/logo.png" alt="Baribaba Logo" />
  <nav>
    <a href="index.html">Home</a>
    <a href="management.html">Management</a>
    <a href="services.html">Services</a>
    <a href="gallery.html">Gallery</a>
    <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>Meet the Founders</h1>
  <p>The people behind Baribaba’s vision to simplify real estate for everyone</p>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="founders">

    <div class="founder">
      <img src="assets/images/argha.jpg" alt="Argha Chakraborty" />
      <h2>Argha Chakraborty</h2>
      <div class="role">Founder</div>
      <p>
        Argha Chakraborty is the Founder of Baribaba, a platform built to simplify property renting and buying by reducing dependency on traditional brokers. With a strong vision to make real estate more transparent, affordable, and user-friendly, Argha focuses on creating tech-driven solutions that connect property owners and seekers directly. His leadership is driven by innovation, trust, and customer-first values.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="founder">
      <img src="assets/images/soumik.jpg" alt="Soumik Pramanik" />
      <h2>Soumik Pramanik</h2>
      <div class="role">Co-Founder</div>
      <p>
        Soumik Pramanik is the Co-Founder of Baribaba and a key force behind its operations and growth strategy. He plays an important role in coordination, execution, and partner management. With a practical approach and strong teamwork mindset, Soumik ensures smooth operations while supporting Baribaba’s mission to reshape the real estate experience.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="vision">
    <h3>Our Shared Vision</h3>
    <p>
      Together, the founders of Baribaba aim to create a transparent, trustworthy, and technology-driven real estate platform that puts people first. From students and families to professionals and businesses, Baribaba is built to serve everyone — making property decisions simpler, smarter, and stress-free.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 Baribaba. All Rights Reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
